{"tid":534842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國客湧上水辦年貨買一喼金莎 深圳女：香港堅啲平啲","createTime":"2018-01-20T08:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T18:12:44.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a64ae19cb8a67875d559f045bd61d6af186c5b2f","tid":534842,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T08:34:58.000Z","msg":"新年將近，大批內地旅客趁周末來港辦年貨，上水新康街一帶藥房人潮洶湧，幾乎一人一喼，藥房在店門擺出一排朱古力、曲奇禮盒陣勢，內地旅客紛紛搜購。來自廣州林小姐指，在香港買金莎較便宜，見到有人買足足一喼金莎，「好似唔駛錢咁」。 來自深圳陳小姐亦買幾盒金莎，「（香港）金莎堅啲平啲」。<br />\n<br />\n內地旅客除了狂掃朱古力，開心果亦是搶購貨品，在上水廣場7樓的樓上燕窩莊逼滿遊客，遊客在商場地下排隊搭電梯，店舖安排顧客排隊入場，店外中午已貼出通告指開心果「此貨暫缺」，要明日才補貨。內地旅客廖先生一口氣購買12包開心果，他讚香港出售開心果味道和品質較佳，每包39元亦較內地便宜。郝小姐亦買了幾包開心果和其他堅果，她認為香港開心果口味比較好。<br />\n<br />\n而水貨客周末未見急增，藥房仍然有一定人排隊買奶粉，有食肆東主指，水貨客情況暫時變化不大，晚上有藥房貨物放在街道，但日間問題不大。上水居民彭先生指，原本上水已經多遊客，近期感覺更擠逼，他認為大批旅客來港辦年貨，可能對香港貨有信心，但自己不會在當區辦年貨，因為太擠逼。<br />\n<br />\n大批內地客在過年前來港購物，來自深圳楊小姐與朋友一口氣購買40盒金莎，她指用來送給客戶，自己亦買了一部iPhone 8，估計消費逾萬元。同樣來自深圳譚小姐指，自己買了千多元零食分送親友，主要是朱古力和餅乾，她指每年僅年初和年尾來港購物，今年人潮特別多，排隊等了很長時間，眼霜等化妝品都缺貨。對於大批遊客買金莎，她認為與內地打貪不能送紅包有關，於是改送禮盒、食物。來自深圳蘇小姐來港辦年貨，買了幾盒糖果禮盒、幾盒金莎，她估計消費3,000多元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/163433_33ebf90c3dd2095a235b9ab7de7abfd8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F163433_33ebf90c3dd2095a235b9ab7de7abfd8.png&h=7fa7e760&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/163436_e7e5f205c7998b22519171ff9a0e15ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F163436_e7e5f205c7998b22519171ff9a0e15ca.png&h=82eb69bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/163445_29f24af4fdebb45af19a5cdd15ef443b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F163445_29f24af4fdebb45af19a5cdd15ef443b.png&h=de7903de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/163446_f9b6c503fa5054c95f4ad8c538dc6d7b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F163446_f9b6c503fa5054c95f4ad8c538dc6d7b.png&h=01b2399f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/163447_674a3a85ca6aa773f19d56c1aabc28f6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F163447_674a3a85ca6aa773f19d56c1aabc28f6.png&h=1ceb4215&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/163450_cf0ebf44f54992e18d4ff1861814de76.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F163450_cf0ebf44f54992e18d4ff1861814de76.png&h=a580791f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/163453_364b46924748a79e3b0d901b3290d2f4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F163453_364b46924748a79e3b0d901b3290d2f4.png&h=e56aa190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180120/57731603\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180120%2F57731603&d=VATVdNANZ2xGWoSs%2F9z2dY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=d1da5247\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180120%2F57731603&h=f2cd63de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180120/57731603</a>"},{"pid":"da6fcbd7fd6eb1b7a9c1b062d4d1a66c7d6a9609","tid":534842,"uid":82125,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T08:38:37.000Z","msg":"深圳賣既金莎仲未超越香港水平？真落後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266576949440bf91fa17fbecbb00fe145d9194d9","tid":534842,"uid":61675,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"